    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooking, preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Drain your<strong> beetroot </strong>in a colander over the sink</p><p>Chop<strong> half</strong> the <strong>beetroot</strong> into small bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>remaining beetroot </strong>to a <strong>food processor </strong>with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water </strong>and blend until a smooth purée forms</p>",
