      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>beetroot risotto</strong> with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>crumbled goats' cheese</strong>, <strong>roasted beetroot</strong>, <strong>toasted hazelnuts </strong>and <strong>remaining chopped basil</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> dressed salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
